OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FBritain is considering sending
OL,8,Fminehunting drones to unblock Iran's
OL,9,Fstranglehold over a key oil shipping
OL,10,Froute, as Donald Trump called for
OL,11,Fallied warships to protect tankers in
OL,12,Fthe region.
OL,14,FOn Saturday, the US president urged
OL,15,Fthe UK and other nations to send naval
OL,16,Fvessels to help secure the Strait of
OL,17,FHormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
