PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FTehran is blockading the narrow sea
OL,8,Fpassage out of the Persian Gulf,
OL,9,Fstemming the flow from the Middle East
OL,10,Fand pushing up energy prices across
OL,11,Fthe globe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
