PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FIn an appeal to nations affected by
OL,8,Fthe price spikes on his Truth Social
OL,9,Fplatform, Mr Trump said: "Hopefully
OL,10,FChina, France, Japan, South Korea, the
OL,11,FUK, and others, that are affected by
OL,12,Fthis artificial constraint will send
OL,13,Fships to the area so that the Hormuz
OL,14,FStrait will no longer be a threat by a
OL,15,Fnation that has been totally
OL,16,Fdecapitated.
OL,26,@qD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,F"In the meantime, the United States
OL,8,Fwill be bombing the hell out of the
OL,9,Fshoreline and continually shooting
OL,10,FIranian boats and ships out of the
OL,11,Fwater. One way or the other, we will
OL,12,Fsoon get the Hormuz Strait OPEN, SAFE,
OL,13,Fand FREE!"
OL,15,FThe Ministry of Defence responded by
OL,16,Fsaying "a range of options" were being
OL,17,Fconsidered to secure shipping through
OL,18,Fthe strait, where some 20% of the
OL,19,Fworld's oil ordinarily passes through
OL,20,Feach day.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]xD@HOUxD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FNumerous oil tankers have come under
OL,8,Ffire as they attempted to pass through
OL,9,Fsince the start of the conflict.
OL,11,FThere have also been growing concerns
OL,12,Fthat Iran has starting placing sea
OL,13,Fmines in the strait to frustrate
OL,14,Fshipping.
OL,16,FMilitary chiefs are now considering
OL,17,Fthe deployment of minehunting drones
OL,18,Fto deal with that threat, it is
OL,19,Funderstood.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FThe Sunday Times, which first reported
OL,8,Fthe proposals, said the minehunting
OL,9,Fdrones could be deployed from the
OL,10,FRoyal Navy's Mine and Threat
OL,11,FExploitation Group, which is currently
OL,12,Fin the Middle East.
OL,14,FBut the newspaper said it is not known
OL,15,Fhow many drones are in service and
OL,16,Fwhich could be deployed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
