OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FThe Sunday Telegraph meanwhile
OL,8,Freported that interceptor drones, made
OL,9,Fin the UK for Ukraine to use against
OL,10,FRussia, could also be used against
OL,11,FIran's aerial Shahed drones.
OL,13,FThat option is understood to be at a
OL,14,Fmuch earlier stage of consideration.
OL,16,FMojtaba Khamenei, Iran's new supreme
OL,17,Fleader, vowed to keep blocking the
OL,18,FStrait of Hormuz as a means of
OL,19,Fpressuring the US in his first public
OL,20,Fstatement this week.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
