OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FMr Trump has threatened to "wipe out"
OL,8,FKharg Island, a vital part of Iran's
OL,9,Foil infrastructure, should Tehran not
OL,10,Freopen the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,12,FThe US has already "totally
OL,13,Fobliterated" a series of military
OL,14,Ftargets on the island in recent
OL,15,Fstrikes which Mr Trump described as
OL,16,F"one of the most powerful bombing
OL,17,Fraids in the history of the Middle
OL,18,FEast".
OL,20,FElsewhere in events related to the
OL,21,FMiddle East crisis:
OL,26,@oD@\OUoD@eO]tD@TOUuD@LO]xD@AOUzD@EO]
