OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,F` The Metropolitan Police is preparing
OL,8,Ffor a "difficult public order"
OL,9,Fenvironment on Sunday, when there will
OL,10,Fbe an Al Quds Day demonstration in
OL,11,FLondon. At least 1,000 officers have
OL,12,Fbeen drafted in to manage crowds
OL,13,Fexpected to reach about 12,000 people.
OL,15,F` Fruit and vegetable producers have
OL,16,Fwarned they may be forced to halt
OL,17,Fproduction and end the season early
OL,18,Fbecause of the rising price of energy
OL,19,Fand transportation costs linked to the
OL,20,Fwar.
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
