OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,F` Chancellor Rachel Reeves has hinted
OL,8,Fthere may be some form of financial
OL,9,Fhelp for homes who use heating oil,
OL,10,Fwhich is not protected by the energy
OL,11,Fprice cap.
OL,13,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband said the
OL,14,Flatest rise in oil prices due to
OL,15,Fglobal events showed the importance of
OL,16,Fmoving towards renewable energy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
