OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,FWriting in The Observer, Mr Miliband
OL,8,Fsaid: "As conflict in the Middle East
OL,9,Fpushes up global oil and gas prices,
OL,10,Ffamilies will be worrying about the
OL,11,Fimpact on bills here in the UK. The
OL,12,FGovernment's number one priority is to
OL,13,Ftackle the affordability crisis.
OL,15,F"We will also act on the single most
OL,16,Fimportant long-term lesson: while we
OL,17,Fare so dependent on fossil fuels,
OL,18,Fhouseholds, business and public
OL,19,Ffinances are exposed, and there can be
OL,20,Fno proper energy security for our
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1773558304
OL,3,CMilitary chiefs mulling use of
OL,4,Cminehunter drones amid Iran oil
OL,5,Cblockade
OL,7,F"That is why this Government's
OL,8,Fdefining mission has been to drive for
OL,9,Fclean, homegrown power we can control.
OL,11,F"Global events demonstrate there's not
OL,12,Fa moment to waste in our drive for
OL,13,Fclean power. So today I'm announcing a
OL,14,Fseries of initiatives that we will be
OL,15,Flaunching this summer."
